(490, '6cFS2et4GmGWHAurmFLUzw==', 1, '<div class=\"_3xX726aBn29LDbsDtzr_6E _1Ap4F5maDtT1E1YuCiaO0r D3IL3FD0RFy_mkKLPwL4\" style=\"max-width: 800px;\" data-click-id=\"text\" data-adclicklocation=\"media\"><div class=\"_292iotee39Lmt0MkQZ2hPV RichTextJSON-root\"><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">Howdy there! You can call me Kelvin. I build digital products for brands and individuals and today, I\'m offering to help you <strong class=\"_12FoOEddL7j_RgMQN0SNeU\">free up your time</strong> by taking care of all the tech tasks you\'re willing to delegate.</p><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">Briefly, I\'m a <strong class=\"_12FoOEddL7j_RgMQN0SNeU\">web developer</strong> and <strong class=\"_12FoOEddL7j_RgMQN0SNeU\">content writer</strong>\n who\'s passionate about building products that businesses and their \naudiences love! I\'ve worked at the intersection of marketing, design, \nand technology for a little over 4 years.</p><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">So,\n if you\'re looking for someone to help you create a website or landing \npage with converting copy, or an extra pair of hands to help with \nshipping blog content faster, that\'s exactly what we\'ll work on.</p><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">My skillset you ask? Let\'s see.</p><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\"><strong class=\"_12FoOEddL7j_RgMQN0SNeU\">1] Content writing</strong></p><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">I\'ve\n helped brands engage with their customers through informative long-form\n blog posts, and short-form converting blog posts. I\'m also skilled at \nbuilding detailed product pages that have engaging copy (and are \noptimized for search). (I\'ll gladly share samples).</p><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\"><strong class=\"_12FoOEddL7j_RgMQN0SNeU\">2] Marketing strategy &amp; automation</strong></p><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">I\n will work with you to develop the right brand persona or craft \nappropriate USPs and differentiation points. We\'ll then package all that\n into highly effective campaigns that promise sales growth through \nconsistent customer engagement while keeping your brand top-of-mind \namong your audience when they need it most—like right after they signed \nup or bought a product.</p><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\"><strong class=\"_12FoOEddL7j_RgMQN0SNeU\">3]</strong> Queue the <strong class=\"_12FoOEddL7j_RgMQN0SNeU\">web development</strong> geek</p><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">Did\n someone say code? Yeah... you guessed it - I\'ve built some fast, \nresponsive and awesome websites from scratch using \nHTML5/CSS3/Bootstrap/jQuery/Laravel etc., and using CMSs like Webflow, \nWix and WordPress. I\'m now working on my MERN stack. Anyhow, if you\'re \nlooking for help with web development in general - I\'m your guy!</p><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">Besides tasks related to the above, I\'m ready to help with other areas of your work including :</p><ol class=\"_1eJr7K139jnMstd4HajqYP\"><li class=\"_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz\"><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">Data entry and proofreading</p></li><li class=\"_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz\"><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">Online research</p></li><li class=\"_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz\"><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">Photo editing</p></li><li class=\"_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz\"><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">Other general tasks you’re too bored to do, or lack the time to work on! :)</p></li></ol><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">So, let\'s do it! If you already have a team in place, worry not as I\'ll happily blend in with them.</p><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">Feel free to PM me your question or offer - I\'ll be glad to respond as soon as I can!</p><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">Thanks for your time.</p></div></div>', 1, '2022-11-27', '14:56:03', '2022-11-27 11:56:03'),
