 they need it most—like right after they signed up or bought a product.</p><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\"><strong class=\"_12FoOEddL7j_RgMQN0SNeU\">3]</strong> Queue the <strong class=\"_12FoOEddL7j_RgMQN0SNeU\">web development</strong> geek</p><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">Did someone say code? Yeah... you guessed it - I\'ve built some fast, responsive and awesome websites from scratch using HTML5/CSS3/Bootstrap/jQuery/Laravel etc., and using CMSs like Webflow, Wix and WordPress. I\'m now working on my MERN stack. Anyhow, if you\'re looking for help with web development in general - I\'m your guy!</p><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">Besides tasks related to the above, I\'m ready to help with other areas of your work including:</p><ol class=\"_1eJr7K139jnMstd4HajqYP\"><li class=\"_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz\"><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">Data entry and proofreading</p></li><li class=\"_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz\"><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">Online research</p></li><li class=\"_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz\"><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">Photo editing</p></li><li class=\"_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz\"><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">Other general tasks you’re too bored to do, or</p></li></ol><div class=\"_3xX726aBn29LDbsDtzr_6E _1Ap4F5maDtT1E1YuCiaO0r D3IL3FD0RFy_mkKLPwL4\" style=\"max-width: 800px;\" data-click-id=\"text\" data-adclicklocation=\"media\"><div class=\"_292iotee39Lmt0MkQZ2hPV RichTextJSON-root\"><ol class=\"_1eJr7K139jnMstd4HajqYP\"><li class=\"_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz\" value=\"4\"><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\"> lack the time to work on! :)</p></li></ol><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">So, let\'s do it! If you already have a team in place, worry not as I\'ll happily blend in with them.</p><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">Feel free to PM me your question or offer - I\'ll be glad to respond as soon as I can!</p><p class=\"_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM\">Thanks for your time.</p></div></div>', 1, '2022-12-01', '13:06:01', '2022-12-01 10:06:01'),
(497, 'ijrq/EdZJQN4AFRFMEG6xA==', 1, '<p>Q: Portfolio <br></p><p>A: You can find a few of the projects I\'ve worked on here: <a href=\"https://kelvin.gyrexconsulting.com\" target=\"_blank\">https://kelvin.gyrexconsulting.com</a></p><p>Q: Describe your professional goals within your chosen technical field. How will a Digital Apprenticeship Program help you achieve your professional goals?<br></p><p>A: I have been working towards becoming a full-stack developer as I enjoy building fully-featured cross-platform applications.&nbsp; Working at the intersection of businesses and technology, I have also had small roles in creating converting copy for websites.<br><br>The program would help me develop my skills in web development, mobile development, and UI/UX design. This would give me a better understanding of the entire development process, which would help me create more efficient and user-friendly applications. Additionally, the program would give me the opportunity to network with other professionals in the field and gain valuable insights into the industry. This would help me stay up-to-date with the latest trends and technologies, and also help me build a strong portfolio of projects to showcase my skills. Ultimately, the Digital Apprenticeship Program would help me reach my professional goals by equipping me with the necessary skills and knowledge to become a successful full-stack developer.</p><p><br></p><p>Q: Highlight professional accomplishments that you are most proud of and discuss the positive impact of your technical expertise/skills.<br></p><p>A: I am most proud of the work I have done helping local businesses transform their operations for improved efficiency. I have had the opportunity to create websites, custom ERPS, CRMs and POSs. One project that I am particularly proud of is a web application I developed for a law firm. The application was designed to help them manage a ton of their work including tracking cases and their progress, managing daily tasks and finances. I was able to create an intuitive user interface and develop a secure database to store sensitive information. The application enabled the business to increase their efficiency and productivity. <br></p><p><br></p><p>Q: Describe a situation in which you faced an obstacle and explain how you were able to overcome it. <br></p><p>A: Recently I faced a challenge when I took up a project to develop a web application for a client. The client had a very specific set of requirements that were difficult to meet due to the limited timeline. Despite this, I was able to overcome the obstacle by breaking down the project into smaller, more manageable tasks. Additionally, I was able to leverage my technical skills and knowledge to develop a solution that met the client\'s needs within the given timeline. Through this experience, I was able to learn the importance of effective planning and organization in order to achieve success.</p><p><br></p><p>Q: Describe any volunteer, mentoring, or community activities in which you have participated, with specific focus on how those activities have affected your professional growth. <br></p><p>A: I have volunteered at local tech events and hackathons, where I have had the chance to work with teams to develop and present their projects. Through these experiences, I have been able to gain valuable insights into the development process, as well as the importance of collaboration and communication. Additionally, I have been a mentor to friends who\'re interested in pursuing a career in software engineering. Through these experiences, I have been able to them better understand the software engineering process and provide them with guidance and resources to help them reach their goals. These activities have helped me to develop better communication, problem-solving, and organizational skills, which have been essential for my professional growth.</p><p><br></p><p>Q: Describe what makes your personal journey unique, highlighting any aspects of your background that have shaped your educational, professional and/or extracurricular experiences.</p><p><br></p><p>A: My personal journey has been shaped by my diverse background and experiences. I pursued a degree in Mechanical Engineering but my passion for technology and my desire to create meaningful products led me to pursue a career in software engineering. This combination of technical and creative skills has enabled me to develop a unique perspective on problem solving and product development. Additionally, I have had the opportunity to work with a diverse clientele during my employment and freelance endeavors, ranging from individuals to startups and small businesses. This has given me a deep understanding of the software engineering process and the business side of technology.&nbsp; All of these experiences have shaped my journey and have helped me develop the skills and knowledge necessary to pursue a career in software engineering where I have been able to explore different aspects of technology, such as web development and mobile app development. <br></p><p><br></p><p>Q: After participating in the Digital Apprenticeship Program, how will you leverage your experience and the Techbuddy network to impact your professional growth? Please be as detailed and concrete as possible.</p><p>A: After participating in the Digital Apprenticeship Program, I will leverage the experience I\'ll have gained to further my professional growth. I will use the program to refine my skills in web development, mobile development, and UI/UX design. Additionally, I will use the program to expand my knowledge of the software engineering process and the business side of technology. <br><br>I will also use the Techbuddy network to connect with other professionals in the field and gain valuable insights into the industry. Through this, I will be able to stay up-to-date with the latest trends and technologies, and gain a better understanding of the software engineering process. Additionally, I will be able to share my knowledge and experience with others in the network, as well as collaborate on new projects and ideas. <br></p><p><br></p><p>Q: Is there anything else that you think would be useful for us to consider when we evaluate your application? Please explain. <br></p><p>A: I believe that my passion for technology and my diverse educational and professional background, make me a great candidate for the program. I am confident that I can contribute to the program and learn valuable skills that will help me achieve my professional goals.<br></p>', 1, '2022-12-01', '14:26:38', '2022-12-01 11:26:38'),
