(38, 1, '2022-11-17 10:23:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<div class=\"ql-editor\" data-gramm=\"false\" data-placeholder=\"Edit your post here\" contenteditable=\"true\"><p><strong>Is AI article writing here to stay?</strong></p><p><strong>This photo by Street Kid doesn\'t have to be you. This is caused by writer\'s block and ParrotAI is here to change that.<br></strong></p><p><img data-visualcompletion=\"media-vc-image\" alt=\"May be an image of 8 people, people standing and text that says \'Me off to the kitchen to reward myself after writing 25 words\'\" class=\"x1bwycvy x193iq5w x4fas0m x19kjcj4\" src=\"https://scontent.fnbo2-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/315603027_230432092645908_5241351991545715486_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;ccb=1-7&amp;_nc_sid=5cd70e&amp;_nc_ohc=Etn6skD8NjAAX_1RPX_&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fnbo2-1.fna&amp;oh=00_AfBgY6OgdcrY2SDuXKIBolzkifPpLGfG3hvzxRZaKbX_mw&amp;oe=6379721B\">\n</p><p>With artificial intelligence getting better at understanding and responding to human communication, it seems likely that AI will play an increasingly important role in writing. While it is difficult to predict the future, it seems likely that AI will be used more and more in article writing, especially as it gets better at understanding human communication.&nbsp;</p><p>Let us examine this question in depth. First,&nbsp;let\'s look at what AI is and how it is used in writing. AI, or artificial intelligence, is a computer program that is designed to mimic human intelligence. This means that it is able to understand human communication and respond in a way that is similar to how a human would respond.\n\nThere are a few different ways that AI can be used in writing. One way is to simply use a computer program to generate articles based on a set of keywords that are provided. This is known as article spinning, and it is a way to create a large number of articles very quickly. However, the quality of these articles is often not very high, as the computer program is not able to understand the context of the keywords that it is given.\n\nAnother way that AI can be used in writing is to help humans write articles. This can be done in a few different ways. One way is to use AI to help humans brainstorm ideas for articles. Another way is to use AI to help humans edit their articles. This can be done by using a computer program to suggest changes to the article that would make it better.\n\nSo, is AI article writing here to stay? It seems likely that it is. As AI gets better at understanding and responding to human communication, it is likely that it will play an increasingly important role in writing. </p><p><br></p><p><br></p></div><div class=\"ql-clipboard\" tabindex=\"-1\" contenteditable=\"true\"></div><div class=\"ql-tooltip ql-hidden\"><a class=\"ql-preview\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\"></a><input type=\"text\" data-formula=\"e=mc^2\" data-link=\"https://quilljs.com\" data-video=\"Embed URL\"><a class=\"ql-action\"></a><a class=\"ql-remove\"></a></div>', 'Is AI article writing here to stay?', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', '', '', '', '2022-11-17 10:23:14', '2022-11-17 10:23:14', '', 0, 'http://localhost/parrot/blog/?p=38', 0, 'post', '', 0),
