erstand the context of the keywords that it is given.\n\nAnother way that AI can be used in writing is to help humans write articles. This can be done in a few different ways. One way is to use AI to help humans brainstorm ideas for articles. Another way is to use AI to help humans edit their articles. This can be done by using a computer program to suggest changes to the article that would make it better.\n\nSo, is AI article writing here to stay? It seems likely that it is. As AI gets better at understanding and responding to human communication, it is likely that it will play an increasingly important role in writing. </p><p><br></p><p><br></p></div><div class=\"ql-clipboard\" tabindex=\"-1\" contenteditable=\"true\"></div><div class=\"ql-tooltip ql-hidden\"><a class=\"ql-preview\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\"></a><input type=\"text\" data-formula=\"e=mc^2\" data-link=\"https://quilljs.com\" data-video=\"Embed URL\"><a class=\"ql-action\"></a><a class=\"ql-remove\"></a></div>', 'Is AI article writing here to stay?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '38-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-11-17 10:23:14', '2022-11-17 10:23:14', '', 38, 'http://localhost/parrot/blog/?p=39', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
